<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Rustic Spoon | Menu</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        header { background-color: #2c3e50; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0; }
        header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; }
        header p { font-style: italic; color: #ecf0f1; }
        .menu-container { max-width: 800px; margin: 2rem auto; background: white; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-radius: 8px; }
        .menu-section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .menu-section h2 { border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #e74c3c; }
        .menu-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .item-details h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #2c3e50; }
        .item-details p { margin: 5px 0 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #7f8c8d; }
        .item-price { font-weight: bold; color: #27ae60; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        footer { background-color: #2c3e50; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem 0; margin-top: 2rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>The Rustic Spoon</h1>
    <p>Authentic flavors, crafted with passion.</p>
</header>

<div class="menu-container">
    <div class="menu-section">
        <h2>Starters</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <div class="item-details">
                <h3>Bruschetta Al Pomodoro</h3>
                <p>Toasted rustic bread topped with marinated tomatoes, garlic, and basil.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="item-price">$8.50</div>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <div class="item-details">
                <h3>Crispy Calamari</h3>
                <p>Lightly breaded calamari served with a side of zesty marinara sauce.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="item-price">$12.00</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="menu-section">
        <h2>Main Course</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <div class="item-details">
                <h3>Grilled Salmon Filet</h3>
                <p>Wild-caught salmon with a lemon-butter glaze, served with asparagus.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="item-price">$24.00</div>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <div class="item-details">
                <h3>Truffle Mushroom Risotto</h3>
                <p>Creamy Arborio rice cooked with wild mushrooms and truffle oil.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="item-price">$19.50</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="menu-section">
        <h2>Desserts</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <div class="item-details">
                <h3>Classic Tiramisu</h3>
                <p>Espresso-soaked ladyfingers layered with mascarpone cream.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="item-price">$9.00</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="menu-section">
        <h2>Beverages</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <div class="item-details">
                <h3>Artisan Lemonade</h3>
                <p>Freshly squeezed lemons with a hint of mint and lavender.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="item-price">$4.50</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p><strong>Contact Us</strong></p>
    <p>123 Culinary Lane, Foodville, FL 33012 | Phone: (555) 123-4567 | Email: hello@therusticspoon.com</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
